  "A bungee cord stretches 4 m when a 600 N person hangs from it at rest. What is the spring constant?": "",
  "150 N/m for the bungee cord": "",
  "2400 N/m for the bungee cord": "",
  "600 N/m for the bungee cord": "",
  "4 N/m for the bungee cord": "",
